            <div class="grid1">
                <div class="column">
                    <p>Copa Airlines is an airline based in Panama, founded in 1947 and headquartered in Panama City, Panama. The airline operates its services to 84 destinations in 33 countries in North America, Central America, South America, and the Caribbean with a fleet of 82 aircraft. Copa Airlines is known for its services in business and economy class, frequent flyer program called ConnectMiles and Copa club membership for the airport lounges. </p>
